  </li><!-- #comment-## -->
  <li id="comment-8950" class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn"><a href="http://www.pinkofperfection.com" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">pinkofperfection</a></cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2008/02/consider-it/#comment-8950"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2008-02-05T21:42:00-05:00">Tuesday, February 5, 2008 at 9:42 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I love Feast because it&#8217;s the kind of cookbook that I know yours will be &#8212; filled with stories, anecdotes, and shiny gems of <>hmmm, I never knew that<>. I haven&#8217;t tried this granola recipe and now can&#8217;t imagine why not. Sounds delightful.</p>
