      <a href="https://orangette.net/2008/02/consider-it/#comment-8954"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2008-02-05T23:04:00-05:00">Tuesday, February 5, 2008 at 11:04 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Don&#8217;t rush past February!!  Its my favorite month&#8230; the possibility of spring beginning, valentine&#8217;s day and all the pink that comes with it, my birthday and its just cool that it has either 28 or 29 days.  </></>A note about adding flax seeds whole.  Apparently they just get flushed through your system whole so the benefits are only obtainable through ground flax seeds or the oil, and the most health benefits are available immediately after grinding, so don&#8217;t buy the store stuff but use a coffee grinder (or spice grinder).  </></>I went to school at the University of Puget Sound, so I have a fondness for Crazy Hippies. I&#8217;m one myself ðŸ˜‰</></>Love your blog,</>Karolyn who relocated TO San Francisco (opposites!)</p>
    </div>

