    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>discovering how easy and rewarding it was to make granola at home was a revelation.  since you&#8217;re on a granola-as-gift kick, might i offer a suggestion?  it looks < HREF="http://tannazie.blogspot.com/2006/12/gift-in-jar-maple-vanilla-granola.html" REL="nofollow">especially pretty<> in those old-fashioned wire-bail jars &#8212; might give you a few extra points in the race for daughter (in-law) of the year!</p>
