    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>i totally embrace the hippie moniker.</></>i have nigella&#8217;s &#8220;feast&#8221; but i recently came into a boatload of cookbooks all at once and haven&#8217;t yet flipped through that one, though it looks lovely. i think i&#8217;ll be making this granola this weekend (and reading the book) with the flavors of my < HREF="http://thursdaynightsmackdown.com/2008/01/24/in-praise-of-oats/" REL="nofollow">favorite oatmeal<>.  plus, now i have something to do with the jar of lyle&#8217;s golden syrup that&#8217;s been sitting in the pantry. yum!</p>
