      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn"><a href="https://www.blogger.com/profile/14847460502867356840" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">aunto</a></cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2008/02/consider-it/#comment-8966"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2008-02-07T01:16:00-05:00">Thursday, February 7, 2008 at 1:16 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Great article in March&#8217;s Bon Appetit. Please clarify yeast measurement so I can try this wonderful sounding recipe. The recipe calls from 2 1/4 t yeast (from 2 envelopes yeast) Doesn&#8217;t one envelope hold 2 1/4 t?</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-8966' data-commentid="8966" data-postid="1326" data-belowelement="comment-8966" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to aunto" aria-label='Reply to aunto'>Reply</a>    </div>
