    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Dana &#8211; don&#8217;t you know Lyle&#8217;s Golden Syrup makes the best granola? you can have the best of both worlds!</></>Funny, I posted a granola recipe today too. Must be a February thing. And Nigella&#8217;s is fab&#8230; I stash some in my gym bag to deflect that nasty vending machine!</p>
