      <a href="https://orangette.net/2008/02/consider-it/#comment-8978"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2008-02-09T22:24:00-05:00">Saturday, February 9, 2008 at 10:24 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I love it, phyl!  Granola for Valentine&#8217;s Day?  Too good.  As for packing it to ship, I think you&#8217;d be just fine to pack it in zipper-lock plastic bags, slip the bags into padded mailers, and ship them anywhere.  Granola keeps well for at least a couple of weeks, if not more &#8211; or indefinitely!  (I store mine in the fridge only for the nuts&#8217; sake; they go rancid more quickly at room temperature.)  </></>Happy Valentine&#8217;s Day to you and yours.</p>
