      <a href="https://orangette.net/2008/02/consider-it/#comment-8993"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2008-04-21T12:58:00-04:00">Monday, April 21, 2008 at 12:58 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I can&#8217;t say it enough&#8211;this granola is just <>perfect.<> I love that it&#8217;s not overtly sweet&#8211;much more toasty and with some depth to the flavor. And it does make the entire house smell delicious while you&#8217;re baking it. I&#8217;m completely hooked. I first made a half-batch last weekend and then had to make a second half-batch later that week because dear hubby took more of a liking to it than I thought he would! ðŸ™‚</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
