      <a href="https://orangette.net/2008/02/consider-it/#comment-8994"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2008-05-11T22:31:00-04:00">Sunday, May 11, 2008 at 10:31 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Thank you! Thank you! Thank you!</></>I&#8217;m trying to get into the habit of making more of my own food to cut costs and since granola is definitely a staple in my house I had to give this recipe a try.  Just made my first batch &#8211;>  YUMMERS!!!  So simple and quick to make.  And now I have enough to last me for a month!</></>You rock!</p>
    </div>

