  <li id="comment-8998" class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn"><a href="https://www.blogger.com/profile/01493708300940204826" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">Molly</a></cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2008/02/consider-it/#comment-8998"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2008-06-09T02:17:00-04:00">Monday, June 9, 2008 at 2:17 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Sal, I&#8217;m sorry to report that I&#8217;ve never tried working with Splenda.  You might try doing a Google search with the keywords &#8220;marshmallow&#8221; and &#8220;Splenda.&#8221;  I think that&#8217;s your best bet.</></>Good luck!</p>
