      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn"><a href="https://www.blogger.com/profile/01493708300940204826" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">Molly</a></cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2008/02/consider-it/#comment-9001"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2008-08-11T02:55:00-04:00">Monday, August 11, 2008 at 2:55 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Melody, I wish I could be of help, but I honestly don&#8217;t know a thing about soy nuts.  If you don&#8217;t want to just wing it with them, you might try replacing the nuts here with more seeds.  Maybe pumpkin seeds?</p>
    </div>

