      <a href="https://orangette.net/2008/02/consider-it/#comment-9002"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2008-08-17T10:35:00-04:00">Sunday, August 17, 2008 at 10:35 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Hi, Do you really need to keep it in the refridgerator? I&#8217;d really like to display mine in some lovely glass jars I&#8217;ve got&#8230;</></>Lynne</p>
