    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Molly &#8211; when I read all the comments on your taking a break that talked about granola &#8211; I had to scroll back and find that recipe. As soon as I read it I knew my husband would love it. He was very sceptical on seeing my bag of ingredients on the counter (all about it is cheaper to buy it already made, etc) but after tasting just a sample he loves it and is definitely on board for more. PS I love Nigella&#39;s recipes too so don&#39;t know why I didn&#39;t find it before. Have you tried her breakfast bars from the Fast Food book? They are also yummy.</p>
