    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Delicious &#8211; I have made this twice now.  I have omitted the brown rice syrup and sugar, I add a wee bit more honey and apple/pear puree(depending on what needs using) and Rapeseed oil.  Pumpkin seeds are a nice addition too &#8211; 1/2 cup almonds, 1/2 cup pumpkin seeds.  Thanks &#8211; we have converted my husband to museli for breakfast &#8211; got to get those heart heathy seeds in somehow !</p>
