    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Making your own granola is so not hippie.  I am farthest from hippie and the one and only thing that is constant in my rotation is granola.  In fact, my 3-yr-old makes it from time to time!  I&#39;m always looking for a new one.  I&#39;m looking forward to trying yours!  Thanks!</p>
